      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Problem Statement"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Online entrepreneurs spend 5\u201315 hours per week writing content \u2014 emails, social posts, sales copy, scripts \u2014 yet most output is mediocre because they're not trained writers and AI tools produce generic content that doesn't match their voice. Elite Writer is an AI writing system trained on their own content and voice guidelines, producing channel-ready copy that sounds exactly like them at 10x speed."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Goals"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Reduce content creation time by 80% without sacrificing quality or authenticity"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Build a personalized writing system that compounds in quality as more samples are fed in"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Cover all content types: email, social, VSL scripts, blog, ad copy, webinar decks"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Package as both a self-serve product and a done-for-you service"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
